  <title>ASTYPE</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">ASTYPE</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">我们添加了一个新关键字，允许您将一个值用 Astype 转换为一个类型，就像 C# 的 &quot;as &quot;关键字一样：</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">FUNCTION</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> Test (oVar </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">as</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> ParentClass)</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">LOCAL</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> oChild := oVar </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">ASTYPE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> ChildClass</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">IF</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> (oChild != NULL_OBJECT)</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;DoSomething()</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#3366ff;">ENDIF</text></para>
  </body>
